https://bored-api.appbrewery.com/

Public API:-
When your server talks to someone else's server through get or post request and then gets respond

BaseURL/Endpoint 
eg - https://bored-api.appbrewery.com/random - here random is the endpoint

Query Parameters
eg - https://bored-api.appbrewery.com/endpoint?query=value&query2=value&query3=value
https://bored-api.appbrewery.com/filter?type=education


Path Parameters
eg- bored-api.appbrewery.com/endpoint/{path-parameter}
it can be id , user name , key
https://bored-api.appbrewery.com/activity/3943506

The data we are requesting is coming back in JSON format-
js object - name:"Shweta"
json object- "name":"Shweta"
js object -> json   json.stringify(data);
json -> js object   json.parse(jsonData);